NOTICE / 声明

This project, "qoder-for-cn-litigation" (中国民商事诉讼专家套件), is an
original work by 游初 (You Chu).

本项目"qoder-for-cn-litigation"（中国民商事诉讼专家套件）由游初原创开发。

This expert suite provides a comprehensive set of AI-driven skills for Chinese
civil and commercial litigation practice, covering the full litigation workflow
from case intake to post-trial review.

本专家套件为中国民商事诉讼实务提供一整套 AI 驱动的技能集，覆盖从案件受理到
庭后复盘的全流程。

